Keep your home clean and free of tracked litter with this Waterproof Cat Litter Mat. Made from high-quality PU material, this mat is designed to catch and trap litter, preventing it from being spread across your floors. The dual-layer design includes a top mesh layer that captures granules and a urine-resistant layer beneath, making it both effective and easy to clean. This cat litter mat offers a durable solution for cat owners looking to maintain a hygienic home environment, even with the messiest of cats.

  • High-Quality PU Material: Ensures durability and long-lasting use
  • Dual-Layer Design: Mesh top layer traps litter, and bottom layer is urine-resistant for easy cleaning
  • Waterproof & Urine-Resistant: Protects your floors and keeps accidents contained
  • Easy to Clean: Simply remove the top layer, discard litter, and wipe clean
  • Versatile Use: Suitable for all types of litter and works with any litter box setup
  • Size: Compact yet spacious design ideal for most cat litter areas

This cat litter mat is the perfect accessory for any cat owner looking to keep their home cleaner and more organized. Its durable construction and easy maintenance make it a must-have for managing litter messes effectively.

  • Nano Hydrophilic Technology: Ensures superior clarity and protection.

Installation Instructions:

  1. Clean the Rearview Mirror: Ensure the mirror is clean and dry.
  2. Tear Off the First Protective Layer: Carefully remove the first protective film.
  3. Spray Water: Spray water on the mirror after removing the first protective film.
  4. Align and Paste: Align the film with the mirror and paste it carefully.
  5. Remove Bubbles: Use a card to scrape out any bubbles.
  6. Tear Off the Last Protective Layer: Remove the final protective film.
  7. Complete the Installation: Your rearview mirror is now protected.

Margin-top = (heroHeight - cardHeight - logoAreaHeight) / 2 + logoAreaHeight

margin-top: 149px;
}

Cards need to have a width set, otherwise they default to 50px or so.
